# Brand portal (IEP / Coaching)

This repo is the **client portal** for IEP and Coaching only. VA Claims stays on `sustainable-website`.

## Sibling apps

| App | Path | Role | Local port |
|-----|------|------|------------|
| Brand portal | this repo (`brand`) | Parent/client UI | **3001** |
| Sustainable website | `../sustainable-website` | Marketing, funnels, advisor/admin, VA Claims clients, enrollment | **3000** |
| SustainBL Copilot | `../sustainbl-copilot` | In-meeting AI package | — |

## Shared infrastructure

- **Supabase project_id**: `cgghmctyygkqzalfhqsx` (same DB/auth for both apps)
- Use Supabase MCP `execute_sql` for schema/data; do not invent another project
- Stripe keys are shared conceptually; brand handles `portal_session_booking` checkout/webhook for extra sessions
- Enrollment + advisor assignment happen in **sustainable-website**; brand reads `advisor_enrollments`, `appointments`, `profiles`

## Routing contract

- IEP/Coaching password/setup links → `CLIENT_PORTAL_URL` / `NEXT_PUBLIC_CLIENT_PORTAL_URL` (brand)
- Implemented in sustainable-website: `src/lib/auth/client-portal-url.ts`, `generateClientSetupLink`
- VA Claims → main SustainBL site URL only

## Scope rules

- Do **not** rebuild IEP/Coaching dashboards inside sustainable-website
- Advisor review, enrollment, Stripe catalog, messaging from coach → sustainable-website
- Parent journey UI → brand
- Track done/left in `TODO.md`; deferred RAG in `README.md`
- Embeddings: EC2 Ollama via `OLLAMA_EMBED_BASE_URL` + `nomic-embed-text`; chat stays on `OLLAMA_BASE_URL` (cloud)

## Theme

- `service_type` coaching → warm accents, “My Coach”
- Anything else in this portal → IEP theme, “My Advocate”
